{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125515379100094464584069.jpeg/urQS7Dfdi0mvLzU9l0AskA8fR9pdlc1LYAX1U2AF9VM\" alt=\"樂宜比堅尼上陣。（HOY《女行團》截圖）\"><figcaption>樂宜比堅尼上陣。（HOY《女行團》截圖）</figcaption></figure><p>3分鐘9秒比堅尼泳衣畫面</p><p>同上集不遑多讓，「福利」畫面是貴精不貴多。《香港01》記者仔細觀察，原來樂宜着比堅尼泳衣的部分，在全集22分鐘15秒之中僅有珍貴的3分鐘9秒！當中有樂宜介紹水上樂園的特色，亦有剪輯在一起，樂宜濕水暢玩，玩水上滑梯，被水射濕全身的畫面。環節的焦點，反而在她玩高空飛索，瘋狂尖叫的場面。女行團｜樂宜Lokyii泰國篇大騷好身材　網民錯重點狂搵收音咪位置</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125515991326265344704281.jpeg/Xc9ev6ukD6RPH2V27DA2XPUUouX-hyZ6Hj0XOB49Fzg\" alt=\"樂宜比堅尼上陣濕身瀡滑梯。（HOY《女行團》截圖）\"><figcaption>樂宜比堅尼上陣濕身瀡滑梯。（HOY《女行團》截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125515988356567040248761.jpeg/KrA41P1i7kvxGn8z6SCaB8jWJ18TeKM2MjrNMzI6zTM\" alt=\"樂宜比堅尼上陣濕身瀡滑梯。（HOY《女行團》截圖）\"><figcaption>樂宜比堅尼上陣濕身瀡滑梯。（HOY《女行團》截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125515985856630784102564.jpeg/zhakRJE1FsY5PHDcZlHxLsct_tbG4LWXyFR2IshUdiI\" alt=\"樂宜玩高空飛索叫到拆天。（HOY《女行團》截圖）\"><figcaption>樂宜玩高空飛索叫到拆天。（HOY《女行團》截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125515983193116672179806.jpeg/NcPLTCLCz1lCNWcLu5m_g0m1oO1dBzTiyyrJvssqyb4\" alt=\"樂宜玩高空飛索叫到拆天。（HOY《女行團》截圖）\"><figcaption>樂宜玩高空飛索叫到拆天。（HOY《女行團》截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125515993733926912314256.jpeg/S6ziDqqNH2qP89xiG5g7HglQn6lH5-YO-pJpjvqSaY4\" alt=\"樂宜玩濕身瀡滑梯。（HOY《女行團》截圖）\"><figcaption>樂宜玩濕身瀡滑梯。（HOY《女行團》截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125515991380791296632751.jpeg/eSOuREFdxFYiPzMUa9qBJ5GpGANjBvsAv56Jk7-eiZM\" alt=\"樂宜玩濕身瀡滑梯。（HOY《女行團》截圖）\"><figcaption>樂宜玩濕身瀡滑梯。（HOY《女行團》截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125515988268486656472806.jpeg/zBb2T0iitvD45l-uYSzX-Bwo3mEIb